{"tid":971950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［婚迷14年］美國女植物人遭強姦誕嬰","createTime":"2019-01-07T04:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T04:51:14.000Z","uid":41351,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a32a3ae8decb35c753716927c8edccba742daa3e","tid":971950,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"昏迷至少14年　美國女植物人遭性侵兼誕嬰　生父身份未明<br />\n<br />\n熱爆話題<br />\n撰文：喬納森<br />\n2019-01-05 17:14<br />\n最後更新日期：2019-01-06 10:05<br />\n美國發生令人髮指的性侵案。一名在醫護中心昏迷卧床至少14年的女植物人竟然懷孕，至上月底產嬰，醫護人員才如夢初醒，揭發女病人遭性侵事件，當地警方經初步了解，發現案發前男員工可以自由進入所有女病人的病房，存在嚴重保安漏洞，正循嬰兒的DNA追查強姦犯的身份。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53nW7o9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53nW7o9.png&h=be74ff2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"083d184dac172cb2eba3c89f468282dd55740e90","tid":971950,"uid":133563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:49:34.000Z","msg":"諗起Kill bill。有條仆街俾錢醫護人員，人去屌昏迷女主角。"},{"pid":"9701e4a029e5b49871f7d875aa176277dfe81f2d","tid":971950,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"標題唔該刪走地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176a40052aa1302bcb03effbecdc40e723122fbd","tid":971950,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"kill bill<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5051d62c1a0b57ce089f0f0ab74f593fff0ed4","tid":971950,"uid":151245,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"個植物人好慘 睇住自己身體俾人屌緊但咩都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fab6c316aff8efe189678a325ade10c726e8b74","tid":971950,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"Time stop<im